<div class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
        
        
            <h4 class="card-title">
                Cross-diagnosis Psychiatric Neuroimaging
            </h4>
        
        
        <div class="card-text">
            <p>Taking charge of the Psychiatric Imaging Center (PIC) at the Shanghai Mental Health Center, we have constructed a cross-mental disorder neuroimaging database.</p>

<p>Currently, the database posses 7000+ samples of neuroimaging data, covering 10+ major diagnosis categories. We are working on common and specific neuroimaging features across mental disorders.</p>

        </div>
        
